4:["$","p",null,{"className":"text-base leading-8 text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-200","children":"Systematic Investment Plans help investors spread contributions across time, reduce timing pressure, and build discipline. The real advantage is consistency: even modest monthly amounts can grow meaningfully when they stay invested through market cycles."}]
5:["$","section","What a SIP actually does",{"id":"what-a-sip-actually-does","className":"interactive-panel rounded-[28px] p-6","children":[["$","h2",null,{"className":"text-2xl font-semibold text-slate-950 dark:text-slate-50","children":"What a SIP actually does"}],["$","div",null,{"className":"mt-4 space-y-4 text-sm leading-7 text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-300","children":[["$","p","A SIP is a contribution method, not a separate product. You pick a mutual fund and invest a fixed amount on a regular schedule, usually every month.",{"children":"A SIP is a contribution method, not a separate product. You pick a mutual fund and invest a fixed amount on a regular schedule, usually every month."}],["$","p","Because purchases happen across many dates, your average cost gets smoothed over time. That does not remove market risk, but it can make long-term investing easier to stick with.",{"children":"Because purchases happen across many dates, your average cost gets smoothed over time. That does not remove market risk, but it can make long-term investing easier to stick with."}]]}],["$","ul",null,{"className":"mt-4 space-y-2 text-sm leading-7 text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-300","children":[["$","li","Helps build investing discipline",{"className":"rounded-2xl bg-slate-50 px-4 py-3 dark:bg-slate-900","children":"Helps build investing discipline"}],["$","li","Reduces pressure to guess the perfect entry point",{"className":"rounded-2xl bg-slate-50 px-4 py-3 dark:bg-slate-900","children":"Reduces pressure to guess the perfect entry point"}],["$","li","Works well for salaried and recurring-income households",{"className":"rounded-2xl bg-slate-50 px-4 py-3 dark:bg-slate-900","children":"Works well for salaried and recurring-income households"}]]}]]}]
6:["$","section","How compounding supports long-term results",{"id":"how-compounding-supports-long-term-results","className":"interactive-panel rounded-[28px] p-6","children":[["$","h2",null,{"className":"text-2xl font-semibold text-slate-950 dark:text-slate-50","children":"How compounding supports long-term results"}],["$","div",null,{"className":"mt-4 space-y-4 text-sm leading-7 text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-300","children":[["$","p","Compounding matters most when contributions stay consistent and returns are allowed to remain invested. The earlier you begin, the longer your capital has to work.",{"children":"Compounding matters most when contributions stay consistent and returns are allowed to remain invested. The earlier you begin, the longer your capital has to work."}],["$","p","Small delays can have a larger impact than many beginners expect. Increasing a SIP gradually over time can be just as powerful as chasing higher returns.",{"children":"Small delays can have a larger impact than many beginners expect. Increasing a SIP gradually over time can be just as powerful as chasing higher returns."}]]}],["$","ul",null,{"className":"mt-4 space-y-2 text-sm leading-7 text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-300","children":[["$","li","Time in the market often matters more than timing the market",{"className":"rounded-2xl bg-slate-50 px-4 py-3 dark:bg-slate-900","children":"Time in the market often matters more than timing the market"}],["$","li","Annual step-ups can accelerate corpus growth",{"className":"rounded-2xl bg-slate-50 px-4 py-3 dark:bg-slate-900","children":"Annual step-ups can accelerate corpus growth"}],["$","li","Stopping and restarting too often weakens the compounding effect",{"className":"rounded-2xl bg-slate-50 px-4 py-3 dark:bg-slate-900","children":"Stopping and restarting too often weakens the compounding effect"}]]}]]}]
7:["$","section","What to review before starting a SIP",{"id":"what-to-review-before-starting-a-sip","className":"interactive-panel rounded-[28px] p-6","children":[["$","h2",null,{"className":"text-2xl font-semibold text-slate-950 dark:text-slate-50","children":"What to review before starting a SIP"}],["$","div",null,{"className":"mt-4 space-y-4 text-sm leading-7 text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-300","children":[["$","p","Match the fund category to your goal, timeline, and comfort with volatility. Emergency funds and short-term needs should usually stay separate from equity SIPs.",{"children":"Match the fund category to your goal, timeline, and comfort with volatility. Emergency funds and short-term needs should usually stay separate from equity SIPs."}],["$","p","Fees, taxation, and exit rules also matter. A calculator can help estimate ranges, but the actual outcome depends on returns, duration, and staying invested.",{"children":"Fees, taxation, and exit rules also matter. A calculator can help estimate ranges, but the actual outcome depends on returns, duration, and staying invested."}]]}],["$","ul",null,{"className":"mt-4 space-y-2 text-sm leading-7 text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-300","children":[["$","li","Set a goal and expected timeline first",{"className":"rounded-2xl bg-slate-50 px-4 py-3 dark:bg-slate-900","children":"Set a goal and expected timeline first"}],["$","li","Choose a contribution amount you can sustain",{"className":"rounded-2xl bg-slate-50 px-4 py-3 dark:bg-slate-900","children":"Choose a contribution amount you can sustain"}],["$","li","Review performance and allocation periodically, not emotionally",{"className":"rounded-2xl bg-slate-50 px-4 py-3 dark:bg-slate-900","children":"Review performance and allocation periodically, not emotionally"}]]}]]}]
8:["$","section",null,{"className":"interactive-panel rounded-[28px] p-6","children":[["$","h2",null,{"className":"text-2xl font-semibold text-slate-950 dark:text-slate-50","children":"Frequently asked questions"}],["$","div",null,{"className":"mt-4 space-y-4","children":[["$","div","Is a SIP guaranteed to make money?",{"className":"rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-4 dark:border-slate-700 dark:bg-slate-950","children":[["$","h3",null,{"className":"text-base font-semibold text-slate-900 dark:text-slate-100","children":"Is a SIP guaranteed to make money?"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"mt-2 text-sm leading-7 text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-300","children":"No. A SIP reduces timing pressure, but the underlying investment can still rise or fall. Returns depend on the fund, market conditions, and time horizon."}]]}],["$","div","Should I stop my SIP when markets fall?",{"className":"rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-4 dark:border-slate-700 dark:bg-slate-950","children":[["$","h3",null,{"className":"text-base font-semibold text-slate-900 dark:text-slate-100","children":"Should I stop my SIP when markets fall?"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"mt-2 text-sm leading-7 text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-300","children":"Not automatically. For long-term goals, market declines can mean future purchases happen at lower prices. Decisions should be tied to your goal and risk plan, not short-term fear."}]]}]]}]]}]
